tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE FamousMusiciansCollaborations (
  artist_name VARCHAR(255),
  collaboration_artist VARCHAR(255),
  collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
  collaboration_year INT
)
CREATE TABLE musicians ( musician_id INT PRIMARY KEY, musician_name TEXT, genre TEXT );

CREATE TABLE collaborations ( collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY, musician_id INT, collaborator_id INT, collaboration_date DATE, FOREIGN KEY (musician_id) REFERENCES musicians(musician_id), FOREIGN KEY (collaborator_id) REFERENCES musicians(musician_id) );
CREATE TABLE songs ( song_id INT PRIMARY KEY, musician_id INT, song_title TEXT, release_date DATE, FOREIGN KEY (musician_id) REFERENCES musicians(musician_id) );

CREATE TABLE Musicians (
    musician_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    musician_name VARCHAR(50),
    birth_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Artists (
    artist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    artist_name VARCHAR(50),
    genre VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Albums (
    album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    album_name VARCHAR(50),
    release_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    musician_id INT,
    artist_id INT,
    album_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (musician_id) REFERENCES Musicians(musician_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (artist_id) REFERENCES Artists(artist_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (album_id) REFERENCES Albums(album_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Musicians (
 musician_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 musician_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 musician_genre VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
 collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 musician_id1 INT NOT NULL,
 musician_id2 INT NOT NULL,
 collaboration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Songs (
 song_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 song_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 song_genre VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Albums (
 album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 album_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 release_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE BandMembers (
 band_id INT NOT NULL,
 musician_id INT NOT NULL
)
